# Side-by-Side Comparison

| Aspect | Governance | Management | Leadership |
|---------|------------|------------|------------|
| Primary Purpose | Provide strategic direction and oversight | Execute organizational strategy | Inspire and influence people |
| Main Question | Are we doing the right things? | How do we do things right? | How do we inspire people to achieve success? |
| Primary Focus | Strategy, accountability, oversight | Operations, execution, coordination | Vision, culture, people |
| Time Horizon | Long-term | Medium to short-term | Both short and long-term |
| Decision Scope | Strategic decisions | Operational decisions | People and organizational direction |
| Accountability | Accountable to owners and stakeholders | Accountable to governance | Accountable through influence and results |
| Success Measurement | Achievement of strategic objectives | Operational performance | Employee engagement, innovation, organizational culture |
| Typical Participants | Board of Directors, Governing Boards | Executives, Department Managers, Project Managers | Leaders at every organizational level |

